row.entry:
Amounts you received from the sales of livestock and other items you bought specifically
for resale. Do not include sales of livestock held for breeding, dairy purposes, draft,
or sport. These are reported on Form 4797, Sales of Business Property.

Other costs not specified on other lines of Schedule C, such as: Clean-fuel vehicles and
refueling property; Donations to business organizations; Educational expenses;
Environmental cleanup costs; Impairment-related expenses; Interview expense allowances;
Licenses and regulatory fees; Moving machinery; Outplacement services; Penalties and
fines you pay for late performance or nonperformance of a contract; Subscriptions to
trade or professional publications.
